# URLSonar Alert action settings

action.urlsonar.param.vtkey = <string>
* VirusTotal API key (needs to be obtained directly from VirusTotal, the Community edition key is free.

action.urlsonar.param.appkey = <string>
* License key for URLSonar. Obtain from www.groundsecurity.com.

action.urlsonar.param.responsehost = <string>
* This is the host that will receive the result response from URLSonar. Response will be JSON-formatted and will be sent to this host.